item.title: Fashion MNIST Case Study
item.description: Fashion MNIST Case Study This notebook is a case study on MNIST Fashion dataset that due to the almost perfect classification of MNIST is now the new point of reference dataset to learn and try ML algorithms on. Click on the button “Run in Google Colab” to run the notebook and step through the code.
